</view>
<view class="view_second">
<view class="view_forth">
    <image src="https://s2.loli.net/2022/04/12/JmfEg2Oclx4B8I9.png" class="image_first"></image>
    <text class="text_second">主食 : 鸡胸脯肉 200g     </text>
</view>
</view>
<view class="view_second">
<view class="view_forth">
    <image src="https://s2.loli.net/2022/04/12/2bZwyRTvAhSL9z1.png" class="image_first"></image>
    <text class="text_second">辅料 : 花椒 3g | 八角 3g | 香菜 10g 
  </text>
    
</view>
<view class="view_forth">
    <text class="text_second">蒜 10g | 姜 5g | 自制辣椒油 4勺 | 糖 1勺 | 醋 2勺  盐 2匙 | 味精 0.2匙   </text>
</view>
</view>
<view class="view_first">
    <image src="https://s2.loli.net/2022/04/12/im3t4v6aMCnPDRc.png" class="image_first"></image>
    <text class="text_first">做法步骤</text>
</view>
<view class="view_second">
    1.新鲜的鸡胸脯肉洗净备用。鸡胸脯肉放入锅中添加适量清水再放入姜片、花椒、八角。</view>
   
   
<view class="view_second">
    2.放入调味料一品鲜酱油、蚝油、糖大火煮起来。鸡胸脯肉在煮的时候会有浮沫切记一定要取出。鸡胸脯肉煮十五分钟熟透即可。
</view>
<view class="view_second">
    3.鸡胸脯肉取出晾凉至不烫手。需要耐心的把鸡胸脯肉撕成丝。自制辣椒油、糖、味精、醋、盐拌匀淋在鸡胸脯肉上。撒上香菜提鲜。
</view>

